{"tid":2013273,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"呢到有無人係鐘意襯衫？一齊黎傾下","createTime":"2020-05-12T07:44:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T13:32:04.000Z","uid":262593,"like":6,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"a27a554dd722441ef18fd1e7544528cfc2619d70","tid":2013273,"uid":262593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T07:44:44.000Z","msg":"襯衫101<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DKDqy7R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDKDqy7R.jpg&h=0c291474&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n夏天到了<br />\n<br />\n我自己最鐘意就係著黑白淨色tee<br />\n<br />\n一來唔洗特別追牌子 簡簡單單 uniqlo 都可以襯得好好睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PUwjDAw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPUwjDAw.jpg&h=7c9475f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n二來有時懶 唔想搞咁多 搭條五分褲 或者九分長褲都ok<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ofnfbWR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FofnfbWR.jpg&h=8cc165a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一般人最常犯既錯誤係唔fit size冋件衫太殘<br />\n<br />\n我建議係新手盡量著哂fit size 同埋舊左既衫真係要換，寧願買十件uniqlo 都好過著一件殘既supreme<br />\n<br />\n有興趣既朋友可以一齊傾下"},{"pid":"4bd3ed70bc9e5a8e2e25080fbc3671f977d7deda","tid":2013273,"uid":4236,"like":17,"dislike":4,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T07:51:24.000Z","msg":"你知唔知有樣野叫oversize<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你果張圖我都覺得著得麻麻 <br />\n但呢個世界唔係淨係得fit size<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以話香港人著衫真係核突又老土<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c21b05609a7aec0c2704cb482a8a5505c208f53","tid":2013273,"uid":262593,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"4bd3ed70bc9e5a8e2e25080fbc3671f977d7deda","tid":2013273,"uid":4236,"like":17,"dislike":4,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T07:51:24.000Z","msg":"你知唔知有樣野叫oversize<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你果張圖我都覺得著得麻麻 